 - Offers both free and collectible gallery spaces to display NFTs across multiple different chains.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-18T15:53:55.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Web3XR</h2><h3>Realms</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.cryptovoxels.com/\">Cryptovoxels</a> - A virtual world powered by Ethereum where players can buy land, build stores, display art, and more.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-18T15:53:55.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>YouTube</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCSNCMWhEojiVjUySdI7J_wg\">M3</a> - Official M3 channel.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-17T12:30:28.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Companies and Cooperatives</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.playko.com/\">Playko Software</a> - VR/AR/WebXR agency and WebXR game development studio.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-17T11:24:30.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Companies and Cooperatives</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://vhiterabbit.com/\">Vhite Rabbit</a> - Parent company behind Construct Arcade.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-17T11:24:30.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Communities</h2><h3>Facebook</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/webxrko/\">WebXR Korea</a> - Korean WebXR group created by Belivvr.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-13T16:19:16.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Communities</h2><h3>Facebook</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/548527285323630/\">WebXR Paris</a> - Companion to the WebXR Paris group on <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/WebXR-Paris/\">Meetup</a>.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-13T16:19:16.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Standout Projects</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://dudes.gatunes.com/\">Dudes!</a> - A 3D voxel engine built by <a href=\"https://github.com/danielesteban\">Daniel Esteban</a>. Features WebXR support, physics, pathfinding, a multiplayer-enabled VR sculpting mode, and more.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-13T16:09:45.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Web3XR</h2><h3>Realms</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://webaverse.com/\">Webaverse</a> - An open-source virtual world powered by Ethereum with support for custom avatars. Focused on digital ownership, an open economy, and interoperability.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-13T16:09:45.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Art</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://vartiste.xyz/\">VARTISTE</a> - A VR app for 2D drawing and image editing, and 3D model texturing.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-13T15:51:52.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Communities</h2><h3>Discord</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://discord.gg/Jt5tfaM\">WebXR Discord</a> - Official Discord server for all things WebXR, with over 1000 members.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-13T15:51:52.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Web3XR</h2><h3>Galleries</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.rarerooms.io/\">RareRooms</a> - Allows you to create immersive NFT galleries with support for multiple different chains/marketplaces.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-13T15:51:52.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Communities</h2><h3>Discord</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://discord.gg/FE8QnDP\">Wonderland Engine Discord</a> - Wonderland Engine Discord server.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-13T00:32:48.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Communities</h2><h3>Facebook</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/immersiveweb/\">Immersive Web</a> - Oldest WebXR-related group, originally made for WebVR.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-13T00:32:48.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Communities</h2><h3>Facebook</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/arvrweb/\">WebXR</a> - Slightly newer WebXR-centric group.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-13T00:32:48.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Communities</h2><h3>Forums</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://forum.babylonjs.com/\">Babylon.js Forum</a> - Official Babylon.js forum.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-13T00:32:48.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Development</h2><h3>Frameworks and Libraries</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.babylonjs.com/\">Babylon.js</a> - A powerful and feature-rich rendering engine packaged into a JavaScript framework.\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://doc.babylonjs.com/\">Official Documentation</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-13T00:32:48.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Standout Projects</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://mixedreality.mozilla.org/hello-webxr/\">Hello WebXR</a> - Made to commemorate the release of the WebXR 1.0 API, showcases some of what's possible with WebXR.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-12T15:53:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Social Spaces</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.rdland.io/\">Raspberry Dream Land</a> - A progressive WebXR events platform focused on inclusivity, radical self-expression, and virtual relationships.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-12T15:45:02.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>YouTube</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/WebXR\">WebXR</a> - Official WebXR channel.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-12T14:53:09.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>YouTube</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCM5HgDdpKgMejq5HX9EoGHg\">WebXR Summit Series</a> - Contains clips, VODs, and other videos from the WebXR Summit Series.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-12T14:53:09.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>YouTube</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgaPCwqmAmre7mW0J7K8IkA\">Wonderland Engine</a> - Official Wonderland Engine channel.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-12T14:53:09.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Companies and Cooperatives</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.rem5forgood.com/\">REM5</a> - Digital immersive experience design studio specializing in education and social equity initiatives.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-04T06:32:05.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Companies and Cooperatives</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.activereplica.com/\">Active Replica</a> - Offers virtual event hosting through Mozilla Hubs.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-04T06:26:17.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Companies and Cooperatives</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://activetheory.net/\">Active Theory</a> - Developed the Dreamwave platform.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-04T06:26:17.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Companies and Cooperatives</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://lagunalabs.io/\">Laguna Labs</a> - Immersive web tech agency.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-04T06:26:17.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>E-Commerce</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://ozoneuniverse.com/\">Ozone Universe</a> - Virtual enterprise platform for meetings, marketing, and e-commerce.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-09-04T06:26:17.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Companies and Cooperatives</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://sketchfab.com/\">Sketchfab</a> - 3D model marketplace that offers a VR previewer.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-08-17T14:08:11.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Social Spaces</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://hubculture.city/\">Emerald City</a> - A virtual event space developed by Hub Culture.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-08-17T12:34:50.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>E-Commerce</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://vrshop.rebuffreality.com/\">VR Cybershop</a> - Virtual storefront for Rebuff Reality.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-08-17T12:16:49.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Communities</h2><h3>Reddit</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/WonderlandEngine/\">r/WonderlandEngine</a> - Wonderland Engine subreddit.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-08-14T13:32:31.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Development</h2><h3>Engines</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://wonderlandengine.com/\">Wonderland Engine</a> - A development platform designed specifically for building WebXR applications.\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wonderlandengine.com/documentation/\">Official Documentation</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2021-08-14T13:32:31.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Web3XR</h2><h3>Galleries</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.3xr.space/\">3XR</a> - A project by <a href=\"https://github.com/microchipgnu\">microchipgnu</a> that has